This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and language models. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these fields are closely related to NLP. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as these fields are also relevant to the study of language models.
